name: Alex Lopez
summary:
Alex Lopez is a 32-year-old gay man based in Los Angeles, California. He studied at the University of Washington and currently works as a software engineer. Alex is originally from Seattle, Washington, and is fluent in English, Spanish, and Japanese. He values honesty, respect, and equality. 

His interests range from skiing and reading to coding and cooking. He also enjoys staying active. Politically, Alex is liberal and he identifies as agnostic. Alex is a Gemini with an INTP personality type.

Alex is interested in forming a long-term relationship, but is open to short-term dating as well. He practices monogamy and is interested in partners who are 27-35 years old. Alex doesn't currently have children, but he hopes to become a father in the future. His other partner preferences include non-smokers who enjoy drinking and may partake in marijuana. Alex has a dog and being active is also an essential part of his lifestyle.
